desc: Sea moss gel irish sea moss gel. Wild, organic handcrafted, vegan seam moss gel. Nature's superfood. Full of vitamins and minerals. Janaican Sea Moss

layout.text:
ORGANIC, VEGAN, AUTHENTIC
Artisan Sea Moss Gel prepared by me, Noel Lattie, from genuine Jamaican Sea Moss. My grandfather and his family have been harvesting this wild, pure sea moss for decades, and have developed this smooth, pure gel recipe which I have inherited and bring to you.
